OL,5, An Ofsted inspection "contributed" to  
OL,6, the death of head teacher Ruth Perry,  
OL,7, an inquest has ruled.                  
OL,9,FThe inspection "lacked fairness,       
OL,10,Frespect and sensitivity" and was at    
OL,11,Ftimes "rude and intimidating", senior  
OL,12,Fcoroner Heidi Connor said.             
OL,14,FMrs Perry, 53, took her own life in    
OL,15,FJanuary while waiting for an Ofsted    
OL,16,Freport to be published.                
OL,18,FHer sister Julia Waters said "urgent   
OL,19,Flessons must be learnt from Ruth's     
OL,20,Fdeath".                                
